X
x,y \in X
d(x,y) = |x-y|
A, B \subseteq X
d(A, B) = \inf_{x \in A, y\in B}{d(x,y)}
(K_n)_{n \in \mathbb{N}}
K = \{x \in X: \lim_{n \to \infty}d(\{x\}, K_n) = 0\}
K
A_0, A_1, A_2
